SCHEMA: materials/reenactment_descriptor.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.materials.reenactment_descriptor
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Persist deterministic replay inputs required for future materialization reenactment.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record reenactment_descriptor
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - structure_id: id
    - tick_range: map
    - ag_nodes_involved: list<id>
    - batch_ids: list<id>
    - seed_reference: string
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- descriptor contents must be sufficient to reconstruct deterministic micro materialization decisions.
- seed_reference must remain stable for equivalent process inputs.
